#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                        <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Learn more on how to "
"automate your business using <strong>Odoo Studio</strong></span>\n"
"                    </span>\n"
"                    <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                        <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Pelajari lebih "
"lanjut tentang cara mengotomatiskan bisnis Anda menggunakan <strong>Odoo "
"Studio</strong></span>\n"
"                   </span>\n"
"                    <br/>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                    It's the heart of your architectural work. It's where "
"you'll track the advancement of the various tasks,\n"
"                    generate new invoices (if needed), and assign tasks to "
"employees and contractors alike. Track your\n"
"                    timesheets, margins, purchase orders, and more using the "
"project menu to quickly access relevant information.\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                    Inilah bagian utama dari pekerjaan arsitektur Anda. Di "
"sini, Anda akan memantau progres berbagai tugas,\n"
"                    membuat faktur baru (bila perlu), dan menugaskan "
"pekerjaan kepada karyawan maupun kontraktor. Pantau\n"
"                    timesheet, margin, pesanan pembelian, dan lainnya "
"menggunakan menu proyek untuk mengakses informasi yang relevan dengan "
"cepat.\n"
"               </span>\n"
"            </span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                    Use the documents app to store and share all project "
"documents. Sub-workspaces get created for each project, and link to these "
"sub-workspace can be shared with customers so that they have a direct access "
"to all produced documents.\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                    Gunakan aplikasi dokumen untuk menyimpan dan berbagi "
"dokumen proyek. Ruang kerja sekunder akan dibuat untuk setiap proyek, dan "
"tautan ke ruang kerja sekunder ini dapat dibagikan kepada pelanggan sehingga "
"mereka dapat mengakses langsung semua dokumen yang sudah dibuat.\n"
"               </span>\n"
"            </span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">A set of architectural "
"services have already been created and can be edited to match the "
"architects'\n"
"                    services.\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                <span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Serangkaian layanan "
"arsitektur telah dibuat dan dapat diedit agar sesuai dengan\n"
"                    layanan arsitek.\n"
"               </span>\n"
"            </span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                The CRM App is designed to let architecture firms easily "
"manage new prospects, called \"Opportunities\" in Odoo. Track expected "
"revenue, manage communications, and never forget to reach out to interested "
"parties. Opportunities get created in the CRM by filling the \"Contact us\" "
"form on the website, or manually by a salesperson.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">\n"
"                Aplikasi CRM dirancang agar firma arsitektur dapat dengan "
"mudah mengelola prospek baru, yang disebut \"Peluang\" di Odoo. Lacak "
"perkiraan omzet, kelola komunikasi, dan jangan pernah lupa menghubungi pihak-"
"pihak yang tertarik. Peluang dibuat di CRM dengan mengisi formulir \"Hubungi "
"kami\" di website, atau secara manual oleh salesperson.\n"
"           </span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Use the "
"Project Menu to quickly access</span></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Gunakan Menu "
"Project untuk akses cepat</span></span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">A reminder to cancel the opportunity is "
"created when the quotation is sent</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Pengingat untuk membatalkan peluang dibuat "
"saat penawaran dikirim</span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Create automated actions to never forget to "
"execute your next steps to keep your business growing, for\n"
"                        example:</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Buat tindakan otomatis agar Anda tidak lupa "
"melakukan langkah-langkah selanjutnya untuk menjaga pertumbuhan bisnis "
"Anda,\n"
"                        misalnya:</span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Once a quotation has been confirmed, a "
"project is automatically generated in the Project app, with associated "
"tasks.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Setelah penawaran dikonfirmasi, proyek akan "
"otomatis terbuat di aplikasi Project, beserta tugas-tugas terkait.\n"
"           </span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">When it's time to provide the customer with "
"an estimate, a quote can be created by clicking the \"New Quotation\"\n"
"                button on the opportunity. These can also be pre-filled "
"using the Quotation Template feature. Quotation\n"
"                Templates allow you to quickly choose a preset that contains "
"sections and their products - especially useful\n"
"                when you're working with similar, elaborate templates.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 14px\">Saat tiba waktunya untuk memberikan "
"perkiraan biaya kepada pelanggan, penawaran dapat dibuat dengan mengeklik "
"tombol \"Penawaran Baru\"\n"
"                pada peluang. Penawaran ini juga dapat diisi otomatis "
"menggunakan fitur Template Penawaran. Template Penawaran\n"
"                memungkinkan Anda memilih dengan cepat preset yang berisi "
"bagian-bagian dan produk-produknya — hal ini sangat berguna\n"
"                ketika Anda bekerja dengan template yang serupa dan "
"mendetail.\n"
"           </span>"

#. module: architects
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:architects.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n"
"                This industry is made for architects that sell all kind of "
"architectural services such as feasibility studies, schematic design, design "
"development, worksite follow-up, energy efficiency assessment.\n"
"            </span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n"
"                Industry ini dibuat untuk arsitek yang menjual beragam macam "
"layanan arsitek seperti analisis kelayakan, schematic design, design "
"development, worksite follow-up, energy efficiency assessment, dll.\n"
"            </span>"

